00:04:59,377 --> 00:05:00,877
-Um, Horio?

71
00:05:00,910 --> 00:05:02,777
-Come on, I'm on
a roll right now.

72
00:05:02,810 --> 00:05:04,777
There's just no way on
earth Seigaku's going

73
