74
00:05:06,744 --> 00:05:07,444
No way.

75
00:05:07,477 --> 00:05:08,410
-Hey, Horio.

76
00:05:08,444 --> 00:05:09,110
-What is it?

77
00:05:09,144 --> 00:05:11,444
